---
export let action = "/submit-donation";
---

<p class="hjemløs">Hjemløse i Danmark</p>
<hr />
<section class="donation-container">
  <div class="text-section">
    <h1>Hjemløse har brug for ly.<br />Vi har brug for dig.</h1>
    <p>
      Hos WeShelter arbejder vi for at give hjemløse et trygt sted at sove, et
      varmt måltid og den støtte, de har brug for til at komme videre i livet.
      Ingen fortjener at stå alene – din donation kan give håb, varme og en ny
      begyndelse.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="form-section">
    <form action={action} method="POST" class="donation-form">
      <div class="donation-options">
        <button type="button" class="active">Støt månedligt</button>
        <button type="button">Enkelt donation</button>
      </div>

      <h3 class="section-title">Beløb</h3>
      <div class="amount-selection">
        <button type="button" class="selected">60 DKK</button>
        <button type="button">120 DKK</button>
        <button type="button">200 DKK</button>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Andet beløb (DKK)..." />
      </div>

      <h3 class="section-title">Vælg betalingsmetode</h3>
      <div class="payment-methods">
        <button type="button">MobilePay</button>
        <button type="button">Betalingsservice</button>
        <button type="button">Betalingskort</button>
      </div>

      <div class="input-group">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Fornavn" required />
        <input type="text" placeholder="Efternavn" required />
      </div>

      <input type="email" placeholder="Email" required />
      <input type="tel" placeholder="Telefon" required />
      <input type="text" placeholder="Adresse" required />

      <div class="checkbox-group">
        <label><input type="checkbox" /> Ja tak, jeg ønsker skattefradrag</label
        >
        <label><input type="checkbox" required /> Accepter betingelser</label>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="donate-button">STØT</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .donation-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 40px;
  }

  .text-section {
    padding: 20px;
    line-height: 40px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 30px;
    line-height: 45px;
  }

  .form-section {
    width: 100%;
    background: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border: 2px solid #2a5bd7;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .donation-options {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: #f2f2f2;
    padding: 5px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .donation-options button {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 12px;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .donation-options .active {
    background: #2a5bd7;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .amount-selection,
  .payment-methods,
  .input-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .amount-selection button,
  .payment-methods button {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 5px;
    background: white;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .amount-selection .selected,
  .amount-selection button:hover,
  .payment-methods button:hover {
    background: #2a5bd7;
    color: white;
  }

  .amount-selection input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .input-group input,
  input[type="email"],
  input[type="tel"],
  input[type="text"] {
    width: calc(100% - 24px);
    padding: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-top: 5px;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .checkbox-group {
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 15px;
  }

  .donate-button {
    background-color: #2a5bd7;
    color: white;
    padding: 12px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 15px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  hr {
    width: 60px;
    background-color: #2a5bd7;
    height: 2px;
    margin-left: 50px;
  }
  .hjemløs {
    padding-left: 50px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .donation-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .text-section,
    .form-section {
      max-width: 100%;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .text-section,
    .form-section {
      max-width: 100%; /* Fylder hele bredden */
      text-align: left;
      line-height: 40px;
    }

    .form-section {
      width: 90%;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .amount-selection,
    .payment-methods,
    .input-group {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .amount-selection button,
    .payment-methods button {
      width: 48%;
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .input-group input,
    input[type="email"],
    input[type="tel"],
    input[type="text"] {
      width: calc(100% - 16px);
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .donate-button {
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
  }
</style>
